caption.p: Chemical composition of Monarda fistulosa essential oils cultivated in south Alabama.

fn.p: RI calc = Retention indices determined with respect to a homologous series of n-alkanes on a ZB-5ms column. RI db = Retention indices from the databases [ 7, 8, 9, 10]. #1 = Plant sample #1. #2 = Plant sample #2. #3 = Plant sample #3. --- = Not observed. ED = Enantiomeric distribution (dextrorotatory enantiomer: levorotatory enantiomer). tr = Trace (<0.05%).
